id.description: Unique identifier for the feedback submission.

properties.description: Additional properties related to the feedback submission.

hs_all_accessible_team_ids.description: IDs of teams that have access to the submission.

hs_all_assigned_business_unit_ids.description: IDs of business units assigned to the submission.

hs_contact_email_rollup.description: Rollup of contact email addresses associated.

hs_contact_id.description: ID of the contact related to the submission.

hs_created_by_user_id.description: ID of the user who created the submission.

hs_createdate.description: The date when the submission was created.

hs_engagement_id.description: ID of the engagement associated with the submission.

hs_form_guid.description: GUID of the form used for the submission.

hs_ingestion_id.description: ID of the ingestion associated with the submission.

hs_knowledge_article_id.description: ID of the knowledge article linked.

hs_lastmodifieddate.description: The date when the submission was last modified.

hs_merged_object_ids.description: IDs of merged objects related to the submission.

hs_object_id.description: ID of the object associated with the submission.

hs_response_group.description: The group associated with the response.

hs_survey_channel.description: Channel through which the survey was conducted.

hs_survey_id.description: ID of the survey associated with the submission.

hs_survey_name.description: Name of the survey linked to the submission.

hs_updated_by_user_id.description: ID of the user who last updated the submission.

hs_user_ids_of_all_notification_follower.description: User IDs of all followers receiving notifications.

hs_user_ids_of_all_notification_unfollow.description: User IDs of all followers who stopped notifications.

hs_user_ids_of_all_owners.description: User IDs of all owners of the submission.

hs_value.description: Value provided in the feedback submission.

hs_visitor_id.description: ID of the visitor associated with the submission.

createdAt.description: The timestamp when the feedback submission was created.

updatedAt.description: The timestamp of the last update made to the feedback submission.

archived.description: Indicates if the feedback submission is archived or not.

archivedAt.description: The timestamp when the feedback submission was archived.

contacts.description: List of contacts associated with the feedback submission.
